# ==============================
# AI SYSTEM RULES
# ==============================

- AI MUST NEVER crash
- AI MUST ALWAYS return a string
- If AI fails → use fallback_reply()

- ALWAYS wrap AI call in try/catch
- HANDLE:
    - 503 errors (overload)
    - 429 errors (quota)
    - invalid model errors

---

# ==============================
# LEVEL 2 AI (COURSE RECOMMENDATION)
# ==============================

- ALWAYS search database BEFORE calling AI

Function required:

search_courses(keyword)

Rules:
- Search BOTH:
    - Course.title
    - Course.description
- Use ilike (case-insensitive)
- Limit 5 results

---

# IMPORTANT:

If no courses found:
→ MUST fallback to default courses

Example:
courses = Course.query.limit(5).all()

---

# ==============================
# AI PROMPT RULES
# ==============================

Prompt MUST include:

1. Chat history (last 5 messages)
2. Course data from DB
3. User question

---

Prompt behavior rules:

- ALWAYS suggest courses if possible
- If no exact match → suggest general courses
- NEVER say "no courses available"
- Keep answer natural and helpful

---

# ==============================
# FALLBACK AI (MANDATORY)
# ==============================

Function:

fallback_reply(message)

Rules:

- If message contains:
    "khóa", "course"
    → suggest browsing courses page

- If message contains:
    "giá", "price"
    → tell user to check course price

- Default:
    → "AI đang bận, vui lòng thử lại sau."

