# ==============================
# CHAT HISTORY (AI ↔ USER)
# ==============================

Model: ChatMessage

Fields:
- id
- user_id
- role ("user" | "ai")
- message
- created_at

---

Rules:

- Save EVERY message:
    - user message BEFORE AI call
    - AI message AFTER response

- API:
    GET /api/ai/history
    → return last 20 messages

---

